            <strong>Key Features of HunterGamers: </strong></span></span>
            <br style="color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;" />
            <span style="color: #FFFFFF"><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif">User Authentication and Authorization:

